PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,FThe 2022 Assembly Election saw Sinn
OL,7,FFein become the largest party at
OL,8,FStormont for the first time,
OL,9,Ffacilitating Michelle O'Neill to
OL,10,Fbecome the first nationalist First
OL,11,FMinister.
OL,13,FOn Friday the DUP announced their West
OL,14,FBelfast candidate for next year's
OL,15,FAssembly Election, councillor Frank
OL,16,FMcCoubrey, with signs saying 'only
OL,17,FFrank can win'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson has
OL,7,Fpreviously expressed his support for
OL,8,Fco-operation between unionist parties,
OL,9,Fstating his hope "that other political
OL,10,Fleaders will see that the opportunity
OL,11,Fto win for unionism is greater than
OL,12,Fany individual party".
OL,14,FSpeaking to the Press Association
OL,15,Fafter his conference speech at the
OL,16,FRoyal Hotel Cookstown, Mr Allister
OL,17,Fsaid "no seat belongs to any party,
OL,18,Fthey belong to the people".
OL,26,@qD@ROUtD@UO]yD@FOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,F"It's nonsense in a PR (proportional
OL,7,Frepresentation) election to say that
OL,8,Fonly a certain candidate can win," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"The beauty of PR, in a sense, is that
OL,12,Fyou can afford the luxury of choice
OL,13,Fprovided, something we've always
OL,14,Fadvocated, you use your preferences
OL,15,Ftotally within the unionist family.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@bO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,F"There are eight to 10 unionist MLAs
OL,7,Fin Stormont today who wouldn't be
OL,8,Fthere but for TUV transfers, we have
OL,9,Fdelivered on that in past elections,
OL,10,Fand all of unionism needs to deliver
OL,11,Fon transfers.
OL,13,F"It's not about party advantage, it's
OL,14,Fabout obtaining the maximum unionist
OL,15,Fvoice, and I want to see a unionist
OL,16,Frepresenting west Belfast, it's been
OL,17,Fneglected, but it's up to the
OL,18,Felectorate of west Belfast not Gavin
OL,19,FRobinson, not the DUP, not Jim
OL,20,FAllister, to decide who that will be.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,F"And they will do that in a PR
OL,7,Felection, making their choice and
OL,8,Fusing their transfers to ensure the
OL,9,Funionist quota that's there is brought
OL,10,Fout and elects a unionist."
OL,12,FAsked if he would commit to not
OL,13,Frunning a candidate in any seat, he
OL,14,Fsaid: "The question of standing down
OL,15,Fis irrelevant to a PR election, you
OL,16,Fwant to maximise the vote of the PR
OL,17,Felection.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,F"That means providing choice with the
OL,7,Fcaveat that people then use their
OL,8,Ftransfers, so it's not about standing
OL,9,Fdown, it's about standing up for
OL,10,Funionism and getting the biggest
OL,11,Fpossible vote for unionism."
OL,13,FIn his speech Mr Allister referred to
OL,14,Fthe post-Brexit trade arrangements in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, previously the
OL,16,Fprotocol and now the Windsor
OL,17,FFramework, which he said were
OL,18,F"building Irish unity before our eyes,
OL,19,Fwhile unionist aiders and abettors in
OL,20,Fthe Executive look the other way".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]zD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,FHe referred to the DUP leader as "Gave-
OL,7,Fin Gavin", deputy First Minister Emma
OL,8,FLittle-Pengelly as First Minister
OL,9,FMichelle O'Neill's "support act and
OL,10,Fbridesmaid", DUP education minister
OL,11,FPaul Givan as "Paul Give In", and UUP
OL,12,Fhealth minister Mike Nesbitt as
OL,13,F"heading for the exit Mike".
OL,15,FThere were shouts of "shame" and "sell
OL,16,Fouts" as the TUV leader spoke of his
OL,17,Fproblems with the DUP.
OL,26,@nD@bOUoD@IO]qD@TOUrD@KO]sD@OOUsD@\O]uD@
OL,26,AAOUuD@[O]wD@VOUwD@\O]wD@bOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,F"Leave the protocol and the dopes in
OL,7,FStormont in place and we will be
OL,8,Fsleepwalked out of the United Kingdom,
OL,9,Fall under the dishonest pretence of
OL,10,Ffighting for the union, while all the
OL,11,Ftime destroying it," he said.
OL,13,FThe powersharing institutions were not
OL,14,Foperational for around two years as a
OL,15,Fresult of the DUP's boycott in protest
OL,16,Fagainst post-Brexit trading
OL,17,Farrangements.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
