PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,FReferring to the TUV's single MLA, Mr
OL,7,FAllister said: "Give me more Timothy
OL,8,FGastons in Stormont and I'll give you
OL,9,Fa political landscape changed forever.
OL,11,F"Give the TUV the clout and there will
OL,12,Fbe no implementation of the protocol
OL,13,Fthrough Stormont, because we are clear
OL,14,Fthere should be no Executive as long
OL,15,Fas there is a protocol.
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,F"To have an Executive you must
OL,7,Fimplement the protocol, to have an
OL,8,FExecutive you must therefore implement
OL,9,Fyour own destruction, to have an
OL,10,FExecutive you must widen and increase
OL,11,Fthe Irish Sea border."
OL,13,FHe added: "The choice is pandering to
OL,14,FSinn Fein or facing down Sinn Fein.
OL,16,F"The choice is partnering with Sinn
OL,17,FFein or divorcing Sinn Fein.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@VO]uD@KOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774113061
OL,3,CStormont 'dysfunctionalism on stilts'
OL,4,C- Allister
OL,6,F"When will the DUP have had enough of
OL,7,FSinn Fein's unfaithfulness to Northern
OL,8,FIreland, their desertion of good
OL,9,Fgovernment and their unreasonable
OL,10,Fbehaviour in lauding the murder of our
OL,11,Fpeople?"
OL,13,FReform UK MP Danny Kruger and Mr
OL,14,FGaston also spoke at the conference.
OL,16,FA LucidTalk poll from January 2026,
OL,17,Fputs the TUV at 11%, the UUP at 13%,
OL,18,Fand the DUP at 19%.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
